[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Heather bell</b></col> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>, <cd>one of the
pretty subglobose flowers of two European kinds of heather (<spn>Erica
Tetralix</spn>, and <spn>Erica cinerea</spn>).</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

